import style from "./CartUI.module.css" import PopupHandler from "../../UI/PopupHandler" const CartUI = props => { const menulist = props.menulist const content = Object.keys(menulist).map((key)=> { return {menulist[key].name} {menulist[key].count} $ {menulist[key].price} }) return (
CHECKOUT CART
{content}
Menu Count Price
) } export default CartUI
